l'm going to miss the sacrifice.

1035
01:26:16,407 --> 01:26:19,205
(Clang) ...whose name
is the lnaccessible,

1036
01:26:19,327 --> 01:26:23,843
whose name is the Black Mother,
mother of darkness!

1037
